Metadata.CommitMsg:
Fix CI/CD for personal repository limitations

- Remove CodeQL SARIF upload (requires GitHub Advanced Security)
- Upload Trivy results as artifacts instead of SARIF
- Remove security-events permissions (not needed for personal repos)
- Delete CodeQL workflow (not supported on personal repositories)

GitHub Advanced Security is only available for Organizations, not personal repos.
